description.en:
What is the project about?
InteractWith - NFTs infrastructure for apps (APIs, SDKs, Dashboard, Wallet) a combination of MetaMask, Twitter and Stripe. 
Plug-and-play integration tools for developers to build on blockchain. Integrate NFTs into any app with only a few lines of code.
NFT onramp infrastructure for Fiat to Crypto - Building a familiar web2 user experience by selling NFTs via credit cards.

What makes your project unique?
Our dedication to accelerate the adoption of blockchain technology by bringing compelling mass-market web3 integration tools.

History of your project.
Secured seed funding
Admitted to launchpad incubation program
Minter development
4 blockchains supported
1 design partnership

What’s next for your project?
Keep building easy-to-use web3 integration tools for apps and games. 

What can your token be used for?
As a payment method within the platform
